How to call the status page up: statuspage/index.html?root=URL
    If no root is given, it loads up from the current dir - provides a convenient way of loading test data.

status.html - enter a username, and it loads the user's data.
index.html - shows a leaderboard of all the students - you can click through to their status page

Data files:

* page-data.csv - defines up the page name and other global stuff
* task-group-data.csv - defines up task groups
* task-data.csv - defines activity titles and grouping, URLs, etc.
* student-data.csv - contains student data - which activities have been done, nickname, avatar, etc.
* themes/name.css - theming files
* avatars/avatar-theme/* - collections of avatars
